@startuml
' BookIT — DFD Level 0 (Context)
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam shadowing false
title BookIT — DFD Level 0 (Context)

left to right direction

actor "Renter (Browser)" as Renter
actor "Manager (Browser)" as Manager
actor "Admin (Browser)" as Admin

actor "Google OAuth" as OAuth
actor "Payment Gateway" as PGW
actor "SMTP / Email Service" as SMTP

rectangle "BookIT System (P0)" as P0 {
  database "MySQL Database" as DB
  folder "File Storage (uploads/)" as FS
}

' User interactions
Renter -> P0 : Browse units, Register, Login, Reserve, Upload profile pic
Manager -> P0 : Login, Manage units, Approve/Cancel bookings
Admin -> P0 : Manage branches, admins, reports

' External integrations
P0 -> OAuth : OAuth sign-in / exchange code
P0 -> PGW : Payment processing (card tokenization handled by gateway)
P0 -> SMTP : Send transactional emails (confirmations, receipts)
P0 -> DB : Read/Write users, reservations, payments, units, branches
P0 -> FS : Store / Serve uploaded files (profile pictures)

note right of P0
  Single-process context diagram (system boundary)
  Use this for high-level overviews to stakeholders.
end note

@enduml
